data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Back on the market! Three bedroom, two bathroom, and three car garage with an open floor plan and a sunroom on one of the largest lots in the community at 0.33 acre. A freshly painted house, inside and outside including the interior of the garage and garage floors. The kitchen has less than one year old appliances, cabinets, pullout shelves, a breakfast bar, a breakfast nook area, and designer-style laminate flooring for easy care. The living & dining rooms are great entertainment spaces with a remote-controlled ceiling fan and plant shelves to display your favorite pieces. The guest bedrooms also have ceiling fans. Between the bedrooms is the guest bathroom with a vanity, custom built-in shelves, and a tub with a shower. The master bedroom has plenty of room, and two closets, one of them a large walk-in. It also has laminate flooring and a remote-controlled ceiling fan/light. The master bath has two sinks, a walk-in shower, a heated rack, and a tub where you can enjoy your relaxation time. The laundry room has a washer, dryer, utility sink, and cabinets. You and your guests will enjoy sitting out on the screened lanai. All bedrooms, the kitchen, the living area, and the patio all have a sound system. Newer items include A/C unit + HVAC system 2022, and Roof 2015. This community offers a golf course, tennis courts, playground, park, soccer field, dog park, basketball, sand volleyball courts, and a baseball field. Zoned for highly rated schools! Countryway is just 15 minutes from Tampa Int’l. Airport. 20 minutes to Tampa City downtown, shopping, and restaurants, 30 minutes to local beaches.
